.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, soy-milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: banana, broccoli, cabbage, spinach
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, french, turkish
House: wooden, townhouse, farmhouse, colonial
 1. the french is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating cabbage##1
 3. the person eating banana is not the turkish##6
 4. the person eating cabbage is not the person drinking milk##6
 5. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
 7. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the wooden house##1
 9. the townhouse house is somewhere between the wooden house and the colonial house##7
10. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
11. the turkish is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person eating spinach##7
13. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | milk      | tea      | soy-milk |
| Food          | cabbage     | spinach   | banana   | broccoli |
| Nationality   | french      | brazilian | canadian | turkish  |
| House     | farmhouse        | colonial     | townhouse   | wooden  |

