.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, grapes, onion, tomato
City: berlin, prague, boston, new-york
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, ship, taxi
 1. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to berlin##7
 2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person traveling to new-york and the person drinking water##7
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 4. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
 6. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 7. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to prague##5
 8. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating tomato##7
10. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4
11. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
12. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person traveling to boston is not the person driving the scooter##6
14. the person traveling to prague is not the person eating onion##6
15. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person eating grapes##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2     |   3    |    4     |
