.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, tea
There 4 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, lemon, pear
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, hiking, reading
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, rock, trance, ambient
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the person eating apricot##5
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is between the fan of ambient and the fan of trance##2
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is not the fan of rock##6
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating pear##7
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5
 9. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
10. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating lemon##1
12. the person eating lemon is not the fan of trance##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk   | tea     | mirinda   | iced-tea |
| Food       | pear   | apricot | artichoke | lemon    |
| Hobby      | hiking | reading | dancing   | drawing  |
| Music-Genre        | ambient | metal     | trance   | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, soy-milk, water
There 4 different types of food: corn, cranberry, cauliflower, pumpkin
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, designer, police-officer, writer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, indie, rock
 1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 2. the fan of electronic is between the person eating cauliflower and the architect##2
 3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
 5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of funk is not the police-officer##6
 7. the police-officer is somewhere between the person eating pumpkin and the person eating corn##7
 8. the fan of electronic is not the person eating corn##6
 9. the writer is not the person eating pumpkin##6
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
11. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the fan of rock##1
12. the person eating cauliflower is not the person drinking fanta##6
13. the police-officer is on the left of the writer##1
14. the architect is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
15. the designer is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | 7up        | water          | soy-milk    |
| Food         | pumpkin | cranberry    | cauliflower          | corn |
| Job           | architect  | designer   | police-officer | writer      |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | electronic | indie          | funk        |

